text: Bubamara (ladybug in South Slavic languages) may refer to: *Dara Bubamara, Serbian singer *Bubamara Association of Persons with Disabilities * The nickname of the runaway bride, from the film Black Cat, White Cat * A soundtrack from the film Black Cat, White Cat * Zlatna Bubamara na Popularnosta (Golden Ladybug of Popularity), North Macedonia popular culture award
title: Bubamara
